Yazi
Tags: file-managers, rust

Fast terminal file manager with explicit chooser and cwd handoff options.

Important note:
Yazi can report the final cwd or chosen files through dedicated output files, which makes shell integration straightforward.

Help head:
Usage: yazi [OPTIONS] [ENTRIES]...
--cwd-file <CWD_FILE>          Write the cwd on exit to this file
--chooser-file <CHOOSER_FILE>  Write the selected files to this file
--clear-cache                  Clear the cache directory

> yazi --help
